    "en": {
      "title": "China to provide 1,000 metric tons of rice",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "China has provided 1,000 metric tons of rice to the Ministry of Education under the program of providing nutritious food to school students.",
        "The objective of this project is to provide one-day meal for 11 lakh students in 9 provinces of the country.",
        "Chinese Ambassador to Sri Lanka Xinghong said that this activity is a special assistance given to students. (a)"
      ],
